a.	Prompt a welcoming message to the user (“Welcome to the letter game”) 
b.	Prompt a message to the user to enter a word. The word must be of exactly 6 characters. 
c.	Manipulate the word by changing the 6 characters. If the input is an uppercase, change it to ‘1’, for lowercase change it to ‘2’. (e.g. 122122) 												(3 marks)
d.	Prompt the user with the manipulated word. (e.g. 122122)	
e.	Optimise the code to use procedures whenever possible (at least 1 procedure). 
f.	Make sure you use proper label names and include relevant and appropriate comments. 
